to bring that to all

00:43:33.309 --> 00:43:34.844 line:92%
of your multi-windowed apps.

00:43:34.844 --> 00:43:37.447
So, maybe you have multiple
windows open in maps, well,

00:43:37.447 --> 00:43:39.449
