installed can support this

00:43:48.425 --> 00:43:51.428
out of the box without
any modification,

00:43:51.428 --> 00:43:53.530 line:92%
so tabs everywhere.

00:43:53.530 --> 00:43:59.436 line:92%
[ Applause ]

00:43:59.436 --> 00:44:03.206 line:92%
So next, picture-in-picture.

